task.summary: First commit, just to see that everything is connected

I started doing the player and coach. I created an abstract page for a personal page and also an interface because I saw that for each stakeholder there are different details that are displayed on the personal page. For example, the player has the date of birth and the coach has a type of training. That's why I created an interface that describes the contract of the two actions together. I wrote most of the code implementation in the abstract department. And the differences between the two I wrote in new departments that are expanding the abstract department. I've added an ENUM of a status that uses the system. Once the user logs in or out of the system, the status changes. I have seen that the status affects actions to be shown to the user in alerts. I have added the types of training the coaches have. I have added group types of roles to coaches.
